w.nme.com/artists/ella-henderson">Ella Henderson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-heaton">Paul Heaton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-and-stereophonics-to-headline-neighbourhood-weekender-2025-buy-tickets-3813158">James 和 Stereophonics 与 The Wombats、The Lathums、Inhaler 等乐队一起成为 2025 年 Neighborhood Weekender 的头条</a>新闻，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
